    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3000630/extras/012d35908a690a62ed406062b27f56a2.avif?t=1721062485\" width=620 height=230 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>The complete collection of Arcade skins created for summer events over the years in the Rivals Championship Series. Characterized by their pixel VFX and retro game taunts - featuring several characters where their taunts are even playable mini-games! Also includes the Kraggling buddy as a bonus friend.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Special Tournament Collection</h2>These skins were originally created for previous Rivals esports events. We've made these skins available on Steam by popular request, and greatly reduced their individual costs by combining them into packs, so players can complete their collections of past tournament-only skins. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Includes all Arcade skins originally created for summer events.<br></li><li> Includes Arcade Clairen, Mollo, Maypul, Elliana, plus the Kraggling Buddy. <br></li><li> Each skin has a unique taunt and look.<br></li><li> Some Arcade taunts are playable minigames!</li></ul>",
